title: Lone Wolf McQuade-Chuck Norris
description:
Movie Description
Chuck Norris is a renegade Texas Ranger. When he meets David Carradine in a violent showdown, it's karate vs. kung fu.

Credits 
Cast: Chuck Norris 
Director: Steve Carver 

Synopsis
Norris plays Texas Ranger/martial arts expert J.J. McQuade, who along with FBI agent Jackson must track down a bad guy who is stealing U.S. military weapons and selling them to terrorists in Central America.

Film Notes
DVD Features:
Film was originally rated R by the MPAA, but won a PG on appeal.

Film co-produced by 1818 Prods. and Top Kick Prods.
